namo, C. and J. Santalo (2013) "Platform competition: Strategic trade-offs in platform markets." SMJ, 34: 1331-1350.   Desarbo, Grewal, and Wang (2009) “Dynamic strategic groups: Driving spatial evolutionary paths.” SMJ, 30: 1420-1439.   Hallen, B. and K. Eisenhardt (2012) “Catalyzing strategies and efficient tie formation: How entrepreneurial firms obtain investment ties.” AMJ, 55 (1): 35-70.   Jay, J. (2013)"Navigating paradox as a mechanism of change and innovation in hybrid organizations." AMJ, 56 (1): 137-159.   Posen, J., J. Lee, and S. Yi (2013) “The power of imperfect imitation.” SMJ, 34: 149-164. 



